criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Inpatient subjects for re-intervention of: hip prosthesis made by ceramic-on-ceramic
             or metal-on-metal, hip prosthesis made by stainless steel ball and knee prosthesis
             made by polyethylene-on-metal;

          -  Autopsied patients with and without IMD;

          -  Covered by a health insurance.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Infection caused by prosthesis resumption;

          -  Professional exposure to metals;

          -  Patient under guardianship.
